item.title: 30 years of celebrity portraits
item.ExtractedText: George Holz's Hollywood Updated 2158 GMT (0558 HKT) September 20, 2015 16 photos: George Holz's Hollywood Photographer George Holz has built his career photographing the stars. In his new book, "Holz Hollywood," he showcases celebrity portraits spanning 30 years. Seen here is Heather Graham in 1998. Hide Caption
